caption: Ummmmmm their wings are so bomb! I always order the sweet cajun wings flavor. You get 10 pieces for like $11 and it's worth it, because you also get celery and carrot stix included with your order. I highly recommend it. Actually we are ordering about 40 to 50 wings for a work event and it's all because their wings are that good in flavor and crisp and everything is just always on point hands down. I hope they open up a wing plus by my house!  My co worker comes here everytime after work and gets herself her regular wings. She's a regular customer, that's how often she goes there and now I understand why.

Relatively new location. Good selection of sauces for the wings. I was told garlic Parmesan was good but it was too cheesy for me. Medium Buffalo and Lemon Pepper were better. Otherwise the menu pricing is good and the place looks well kept and clean. And the lady at the counter was patient and friendly.
(Translated by Google) I loved the food very rich and the lady was very friendly.  (Original) Me encanto muy rica la comida y la señorita muy amable .
Has decent food at a good price. I always bought the specials at their other locations, and this one is no exception. This is most likely going to be my go to for 45 minute breaks.
